Modifying CHANGELOG
-------------------
$ export DEBFULLNAME="Marc Bredt"; export DEBEMAIL="marc.bredt@gmail.com"
$ dch -c trunk/CHANGELOG --package heili --distribution stable --create -v 0.0.2
$ dch -c trunk/CHANGELOG -r
$ dch -c trunk/CHANGELOG -i

